         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">[24 February 1871] ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ In reply to your letter of the 17th inst. ¶  I have the honor to inform you, that the Hon. the Chief Secretary, on my recommendation, has approved of the application of ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">71.02.24</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To William Paton</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">MS 12521 Victorian Horticultural Society, bzox 3401, p. 446, Australian Manuscripts Collection, La Trobe Library, Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letter not found. Text taken from copy in minute book, p. 445.</p>
               </note>[24 February 1871]<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">This was the date the letter was received by the Society.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In reply to your letter of the 17th inst.<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See W. Paton to M, 17 February 1871.</p>
               </note> I have the honor to inform you, that the Hon. the Chief Secretary, on my recommendation, has approved of the application of the Vict. Hort. Improv. Socy,<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Victorian Horticultural Improvement Society. The Society changed its name in February 1862.</p>
               </note> to hold a horticultural Exhibition in the Botanic Garden on the 18th March 1871 this concession being granted on an understanding that the restrictions adopted on form<note xml:id="ftn6" type="footnote" n="6">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">former?</p>
               </note> so similar occasions will be in force. In reference to these and other details I should be glad to make arrangement with you at my office.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">I have &amp;c</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Signed Ferd von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">To Mr Paton</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Hon Secy</p>
